section.def:
week
                (星期) means the period between midnight on
            Saturday night and midnight on the succeeding Saturday night;

paragraph.content:
specify the number of his identity card, if any, issued under the
                    Registration of Persons Ordinance (Cap.
                    177);

specify the period of employment of the young person for each day of the
                    week as fixed by the notice posted up under regulation
                    9(1);
